wikipedia_page.main: Jessica Alves (formerly Rodrigo Alves; born 30 July 1983) is a Brazilian-British television personality noted for having undergone dozens of plastic surgeries to alter her appearance.

link_mentions.page: San Marino in the Eurovision Song Contest 2019
response: Prior to the selection of Serhat, two artists were rumoured by the press to have been in consideration: social media influencer and "Human Ken Doll" Jessica Alves and Russian Daryanna Kraieva. Alves spoke to the press about the potential participation, further fueling these rumours. In response, SMRTV stated that they would neither confirm nor deny the speculation, directing people to wait for the 21 January announcement.
